                        "text": "There\u2019s no time to be bored in a world as beautiful as this.\ud83d\udc99 Is Iceland on your travel bucket list? Follow { @thrillertravel } for daily content.\n\u2796\n\ud83d\udc49Tag your travel partner\ud83d\udc48\n\ud83d\udc49Don\u2019t forget to turn on post notifications\ud83d\udc48\n\u2796\nIceland, a Nordic island nation, is defined by its dramatic landscape with volcanoes, geysers, hot springs and lava fields. Massive glaciers are protected in Vatnaj\u00f6kull and Sn\u00e6fellsj\u00f6kull national parks. Most of the population lives in the capital, Reykjavik, which runs on geothermal power and is home to the National and Saga museums, tracing Iceland\u2019s Viking history.\n\u2796\n\u2014\u2014\u2014\u2014\u2014\u2014\u2014\u2014\u2014\u2014\u2014\u2014\u2014\u2014\u2014\n\u203c\ufe0fFOLLOW @thrillertravel\u203c\ufe0f\n\u203c\ufe0fFOLLOW @thrillertravel\u203c\ufe0f\n\u203c\ufe0fFOLLOW @thrillertravel\u203c\ufe0f\n\u2014\u2014\u2014\u2014\u2014\u2014\u2014\u2014\u2014\u2014\u2014\u2014\u2014\u2014\u2014\n\u2796\n\ud83d\udcf8: @joseramosphotography\u2b50\ufe0f\u2b50\ufe0f\u2b50\ufe0f"
